{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859186175,"sessionID":"ses_2868bc11fffewl4JSNwfkX3FSd","part":{"id":"prt_d7974b9d9001nZFHvMfzFr0BgR","messageID":"msg_d7974a2f80017D5Ab1M47mUsxj","sessionID":"ses_2868bc11fffewl4JSNwfkX3FSd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-422835ab09284967b1ceb63e689296f8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","limit":300,"offset":200},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n200: **权衡**：\n201: - 路径解析的开销稍高\n202: - 可能拒绝某些合法的复杂路径结构\n203: \n204: ### 并发控制策略\n205: \n206: **决策**：文件级别锁，读操作允许并发，写操作互斥\n207: \n208: **理由**：\n209: - 允许并发读取提高性能\n210: - 防止写入冲突和数据损坏\n211: - 简单的锁语义，易于理解和维护\n212: \n213: **权衡**：\n214: - 粗粒度锁可能影响性能\n215: - 更细粒度的锁会增加复杂度\n216: \n217: ### 错误响应格式\n218: \n219: **决策**：统一的 JSON 格式，包含错误码和消息\n220: \n221: **理由**：\n222: - 客户端易于解析\n223: - 便于错误分类和处理\n224: - 支持国际化（未来）\n225: \n226: **权衡**：\n227: - 需要维护错误码映射表\n228: \n229: ## Alternatives Considered\n230: \n231: ### Alternative 1: WebDAV 协议\n232: \n233: **描述**：使用标准的 WebDAV 协议进行文件操作\n234: \n235: **优点**：\n236: - 标准协议，有现成的客户端\n237: - 支持锁定、版本控制等高级功能\n238: - 与 WebDAV 客户端集成\n239: \n240: **缺点**：\n241: - 协议复杂，实现成本高\n242: - 与现有的 JWT 认证集成困难\n243: - 超出当前需求范围\n244: \n245: **决策**：拒绝 - RESTful API 更简单直接\n246: \n247: ### Alternative 2: gRPC 文件流\n248: \n249: **描述**：使用 gRPC 进行文件传输，支持流式上传/下载\n250: \n251: **优点**：\n252: - 二进制协议，性能更好\n253: - 内置流式支持\n254: - 强类型定义\n255: \n256: **缺点**：\n257: - 客户端需要代码生成\n258: - 不如 HTTP/JSON 通用\n259: - 增加部署复杂度\n260: \n261: **决策**：拒绝 - HTTP/JSON 足够且更易集成\n262: \n263: ### Alternative 3: 基于会话的文件句柄\n264: \n265: **描述**：使用类似文件句柄的机制，需要先打开文件，然后操作\n266: \n267: **优点**：\n268: - 更接近传统文件操作语义\n269: - 可以支持更复杂的操作（如文件定位）\n270: \n271: **缺点**：\n272: - 需要状态管理\n273: - 增加客户端复杂度\n274: - 不符合无状态设计原则\n275: \n276: **决策**：拒绝 - 无状态设计更简单可靠\n277: \n278: ### Alternative 4: 分块上传（Chunked Upload）\n279: \n280: **描述**：支持大文件分块上传，支持断点续传\n281: \n282: **优点**：\n283: - 支持大文件上传\n284: - 网络中断后可以恢复\n285: - 更好的进度反馈\n286: \n287: **缺点**：\n288: - 实现复杂度高\n289: - 需要临时存储\n290: - 增加状态管理\n291: \n292: **决策**：拒绝 - 当前需求不需要大文件支持\n293: \n294: ## API Design\n295: \n296: ### Endpoints\n297: \n298: #### 1. 文件上传\n299: \n300: **POST** `/api/files`\n301: \n302: **Headers**:\n303: ```\n304: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n305: Content-Type: multipart/form-data OR application/json\n306: ```\n307: \n308: **Multipart Form Fields**:\n309: - `path`: 目标文件路径（必需）\n310: - `file`: 文件内容（必需，仅 multipart）\n311: - `mode`: 文件模式，八进制（可选，默认 0644）\n312: \n313: **JSON Request Body**:\n314: ```json\n315: {\n316:   \"path\": \"example.txt\",\n317:   \"content\": \"SGVsbG8gV29ybGQh\",\n318:   \"mode\": \"0644\"\n319: }\n320: ```\n321: \n322: **Response (200 OK)**:\n323: ```json\n324: {\n325:   \"path\": \"example.txt\",\n326:   \"size\": 1024,\n327:   \"mode\": \"0644\",\n328:   \"modified\": \"2025-01-15T10:30:00Z\"\n329: }\n330: ```\n331: \n332: **Errors**:\n333: - `400 Bad Request` - 缺少路径/文件，无效 Base64，路径逃逸工作空间\n334: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n335: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n336: - `500 Internal Server Error` - 服务器内部错误\n337: \n338: #### 2. 文件下载\n339: \n340: **GET** `/api/files/example.txt`\n341: \n342: **Headers**:\n343: ```\n344: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n345: ```\n346: \n347: **Response (200 OK)**:\n348: - Body: 文件内容\n349: - Headers:\n350:   - `Content-Description`: File Transfer\n351:   - `Content-Transfer-Encoding`: binary\n352:   - `Content-Disposition`: attachment; filename=\"example.txt\"\n353:   - `Content-Type`: <检测到的 MIME 类型> 或 application/octet-stream\n354:   - `Content-Length`: <文件大小>\n355: \n356: **Errors**:\n357: - `400 Bad Request` - 路径逃逸工作空间，路径是目录\n358: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n359: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n360: - `404 Not Found` - 文件不存在\n361: \n362: #### 3. 目录列表\n363: \n364: **GET** `/api/files?path=/workspace&recursive=false`\n365: \n366: **Headers**:\n367: ```\n368: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n369: ```\n370: \n371: **Query Parameters**:\n372: - `path`: 目录路径（必需）\n373: - `recursive`: 是否递归（可选，默认 false）\n374: \n375: **Response (200 OK)**:\n376: ```json\n377: {\n378:   \"path\": \"/workspace\",\n379:   \"files\": [\n380:     {\n381:       \"name\": \"example.txt\",\n382:       \"size\": 1024,\n383:       \"modified\": \"2025-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n384:       \"mode\": \"0644\",\n385:       \"is_dir\": false\n386:     },\n387:     {\n388:       \"name\": \"subdir\",\n389:       \"size\": 4096,\n390:       \"modified\": \"2025-01-15T09:00:00Z\",\n391:       \"mode\": \"0755\",\n392:       \"is_dir\": true\n393:     }\n394:   ]\n395: }\n396: ```\n397: \n398: **Errors**:\n399: - `400 Bad Request` - 缺少路径参数，路径逃逸工作空间\n400: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n401: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n402: - `404 Not Found` - 目录不存在\n403: \n404: #### 4. 文件/目录删除\n405: \n406: **DELETE** `/api/files/example.txt?recursive=false`\n407: \n408: **Headers**:\n409: ```\n410: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n411: ```\n412: \n413: **Query Parameters**:\n414: - `recursive`: 是否递归删除目录（可选，默认 false）\n415: \n416: **Response (200 OK)**:\n417: ```json\n418: {\n419:   \"path\": \"example.txt\",\n420:   \"deleted\": true\n421: }\n422: ```\n423: \n424: **Errors**:\n425: - `400 Bad Request` - 路径逃逸工作空间，目录非空但未设置递归\n426: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n427: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n428: - `404 Not Found` - 文件或目录不存在\n429: \n430: #### 5. 目录创建\n431: \n432: **PUT** `/api/files/newdir?mode=0755&recursive=true`\n433: \n434: **Headers**:\n435: ```\n436: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n437: ```\n438: \n439: **Query Parameters**:\n440: - `mode`: 目录模式（可选，默认 0755）\n441: - `recursive`: 是否递归创建（可选，默认 true）\n442: \n443: **Response (200 OK)**:\n444: ```json\n445: {\n446:   \"path\": \"newdir\",\n447:   \"created\": true,\n448:   \"mode\": \"0755\"\n449: }\n450: ```\n451: \n452: **Errors**:\n453: - `400 Bad Request` - 路径逃逸工作空间，路径已存在\n454: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n455: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n456: - `409 Conflict` - 路径已存在（对于文件或非递归时父目录不存在）\n457: \n458: #### 6. 文件元数据\n459: \n460: **GET** `/api/files/example.txt?metadata=true`\n461: \n462: **Headers**:\n463: ```\n464: Authorization: Bearer <jwt_token>\n465: ```\n466: \n467: **Response (200 OK)**:\n468: ```json\n469: {\n470:   \"path\": \"example.txt\",\n471:   \"size\": 1024,\n472:   \"mode\": \"0644\",\n473:   \"modified\": \"2025-01-15T10:30:00Z\",\n474:   \"created\": \"2025-01-15T09:00:00Z\",\n475:   \"is_dir\": false,\n476:   \"mime_type\": \"text/plain; charset=utf-8\"\n477: }\n478: ```\n479: \n480: **Errors**:\n481: - `400 Bad Request` - 路径逃逸工作空间\n482: - `401 Unauthorized` - 缺少或无效的 JWT\n483: - `403 Forbidden` - 权限不足\n484: - `404 Not Found` - 文件不存在\n485: \n486: ## Data Structures\n487: \n488: ### UploadFileRequest\n489: \n490: ```go\n491: type UploadFileRequest struct {\n492:     Path    string `json:\"path\" binding:\"required\"`\n493:     Content string `json:\"content\" binding:\"required\"`\n494:     Mode    string `json:\"mode\"`\n495: }\n496: ```\n497: \n498: ### UploadFileResponse\n499: \n\n(Showing lines 200-499 of 1012. Use offset=500 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"**权衡**：\n- 路径解析的开销稍高\n- 可能拒绝某些合法的复杂路径结构\n\n### 并发控制策略\n\n**决策**：文件级别锁，读操作允许并发，写操作互斥\n\n**理由**：\n- 允许并发读取提高性能\n- 防止写入冲突和数据损坏\n- 简单的锁语义，易于理解和维护\n\n**权衡**：\n- 粗粒度锁可能影响性能\n- 更细粒度的锁会增加复杂度\n\n### 错误响应格式\n\n**决策**：统一的 JSON 格式，包含错误码和消息","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775859186163,"end":1775859186172}}}}
