{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775859189569,"sessionID":"ses_2868bc11fffewl4JSNwfkX3FSd","part":{"id":"prt_d7974c71f001DcogVylPR1mncF","messageID":"msg_d7974ba31001HrNFE07ULoBy7W","sessionID":"ses_2868bc11fffewl4JSNwfkX3FSd","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-998e8186ec284c709d6c9dff97875275","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md","limit":200,"offset":500},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n500: ```go\n501: type UploadFileResponse struct {\n502:     Path     string    `json:\"path\"`\n503:     Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n504:     Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n505:     Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n506: }\n507: ```\n508: \n509: ### FileEntry\n510: \n511: ```go\n512: type FileEntry struct {\n513:     Name     string    `json:\"name\"`\n514:     Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n515:     Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n516:     Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n517:     IsDir    bool      `json:\"is_dir\"`\n518: }\n519: ```\n520: \n521: ### ListFilesResponse\n522: \n523: ```go\n524: type ListFilesResponse struct {\n525:     Path  string      `json:\"path\"`\n526:     Files []FileEntry `json:\"files\"`\n527: }\n528: ```\n529: \n530: ### DeleteFileResponse\n531: \n532: ```go\n533: type DeleteFileResponse struct {\n534:     Path    string `json:\"path\"`\n535:     Deleted bool   `json:\"deleted\"`\n536: }\n537: ```\n538: \n539: ### CreateDirResponse\n540: \n541: ```go\n542: type CreateDirResponse struct {\n543:     Path    string `json:\"path\"`\n544:     Created bool   `json:\"created\"`\n545:     Mode    string `json:\"mode\"`\n546: }\n547: ```\n548: \n549: ### FileMetadata\n550: \n551: ```go\n552: type FileMetadata struct {\n553:     Path     string    `json:\"path\"`\n554:     Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n555:     Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n556:     Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n557:     Created  time.Time `json:\"created\"`\n558:     IsDir    bool      `json:\"is_dir\"`\n559:     MimeType string    `json:\"mime_type\"`\n560: }\n561: ```\n562: \n563: ## Constants\n564: \n565: | Name | Value | Meaning |\n566: |------|-------|---------|\n567: | `DefaultFileMode` | `0644` | Default file permissions |\n568: | `DefaultDirMode` | `0755` | Default directory permissions |\n569: | `MaxFileMode` | `0777` | Maximum allowed file mode |\n570: | `MaxPathLength` | `4096` | Maximum path length in bytes |\n571: | `FileLockTimeout` | `30s` | Timeout for acquiring file lock |\n572: \n573: ## Security Considerations\n574: \n575: ### 路径安全\n576: \n577: 1. **工作空间监狱**\n578:    - 所有路径相对于配置的工作空间解析\n579:    - 符号链接解析防止逃逸\n580:    - 相对路径验证（无 `..` 组件）\n581:    - 绝对路径规范化\n582: \n583: 2. **文件权限**\n584:    - 最大模式 0777（无 setuid/setgid/sticky 位）\n585:    - 默认模式 0644（可读，所有者可写）\n586:    - 防止创建可执行文件\n587: \n588: 3. **文件操作**\n589:    - 写入前验证路径\n590:    - 防止符号链接竞争\n591:    - 原子操作（尽可能）\n592: \n593: ### 认证和授权\n594: \n595: 1. **JWT 验证**\n596:    - 签名验证\n597:    - 算法验证（仅 RSA 方法）\n598:    - 过期时间检查\n599:    - 拒绝 HS256 和其他非 RSA 方法\n600: \n601: 2. **请求限制**\n602:    - 32 MiB 请求体限制\n603:    - 防止内存耗尽攻击\n604:    - 操作速率限制（未来）\n605: \n606: ### 错误消息\n607: \n608: 1. **公共错误**\n609:    - 认证失败的通用错误消息\n610:    - 401/403 响应中无敏感数据\n611:    - 详细的错误记录在服务器端\n612: \n613: 2. **信息泄露**\n614:    - 健康端点仅显示服务状态\n615:    - 错误响应中无版本信息\n616: \n617: ## Testing Strategy\n618: \n619: ### Unit Tests\n620: \n621: 1. **文件上传测试**\n622:    - Multipart 上传：成功、无效 Base64、路径逃逸、文件模式验证\n623:    - JSON 上传：成功、无效 JSON、缺失字段、大文件\n624:    - 父目录创建：自动创建、权限错误\n625: \n626: 2. **文件下载测试**\n627:    - 成功下载：各种文件类型、大文件\n628:    - 错误场景：路径逃逸、目录、文件不存在\n629:    - MIME 类型检测：各种扩展名\n630: \n631: 3. **目录列表测试**\n632:    - 成功列表：空目录、多文件、递归\n633:    - 错误场景：目录不存在、权限错误、无效路径\n634:    - 元数据准确性\n635: \n636: 4. **删除操作测试**\n637:    - 成功删除：文件、空目录、递归删除\n638:    - 错误场景：路径逃逸、非空目录无递归、文件不存在\n639: \n640: 5. **目录创建测试**\n641:    - 成功创建：单个目录、递归创建、自定义模式\n642:    - 错误场景：路径已存在、权限错误、路径逃逸\n643: \n644: 6. **路径安全测试**\n645:    - sanitizePath：有效路径、相对路径带 `..`、符号链接逃逸、绝对路径\n646:    - 路径长度限制、特殊字符处理\n647: \n648: 7. **文件模式测试**\n649:    - parseFileMode：有效模式、无效模式、空模式、模式 > 0777\n650: \n651: 8. **并发测试**\n652:    - 并发读取\n653:    - 并发写入\n654:    - 读写混合\n655: \n656: ### Integration Tests\n657: \n658: 1. **端到端流程**\n659:    - 上传文件 → 列出文件 → 下载文件 → 删除文件\n660:    - 创建目录结构 → 递归列出 → 递归删除\n661:    - 大文件上传下载\n662: \n663: 2. **认证流程**\n664:    - 有效令牌 → 成功的 API 访问\n665:    - 无效令牌 → 401 响应\n666:    - 过期令牌 → 401 响应\n667: \n668: 3. **安全测试**\n669:    - 路径逃逸尝试\n670:    - 符号链接攻击\n671:    - 权限提升尝试\n672: \n673: ### Test Coverage Targets\n674: \n675: - 单元测试：>90% 代码覆盖率\n676: - 关键路径（安全、路径验证）：100% 覆盖率\n677: - 错误处理路径：完整覆盖\n678: \n679: ## Configuration\n680: \n681: ### CLI Flags\n682: \n683: | Flag | Type | Default | Description |\n684: |------|------|---------|-------------|\n685: | `-port` | int | `8080` | PicoD 服务器监听端口 |\n686: | `-workspace` | string | `\"\"` | 文件操作的根目录（默认：当前工作目录） |\n687: \n688: ### Environment Variables\n689: \n690: | Name | Required | Description |\n691: |------|----------|-------------|\n692: | `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` | Yes | JWT 验证的 PEM 编码 RSA 公钥 |\n693: \n694: ## Migration Strategy\n695: \n696: ### Phase 1: 实现（Week 1-2）\n697: \n698: 1. 实现文件上传处理器\n699: 2. 实现文件下载处理器\n\n(Showing lines 500-699 of 1012. Use offset=700 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"```go\ntype UploadFileResponse struct {\n    Path     string    `json:\"path\"`\n    Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n    Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n    Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n}\n```\n\n### FileEntry\n\n```go\ntype FileEntry struct {\n    Name     string    `json:\"name\"`\n    Size     int64     `json:\"size\"`\n    Modified time.Time `json:\"modified\"`\n    Mode     string    `json:\"mode\"`\n    IsDir    bool      `json:\"is_dir\"`\n}\n```",